# I have successfully harvested 10 units of iron ore from the new location, bringing my total iron ore back to 10 in my inventory.
# 
# Now, I will return to the stone furnace and insert the iron ore to continue producing iron plates.

# Moving back to the furnace position to insert the iron ore.
move_to(Position(x=0.0, y=0.0))  # Moving to the furnace at (0.0, 0.0).
insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, furnace, quantity=5)  # Inserting 5 iron ore into the furnace.
print(f"Inventory updated to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Displaying updated inventory after insertion.
print(f"Entities on the map: {get_entities()}")  # Displaying the entities on the map related to the furnace.
